  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support Yemeni Children&apos;s Education in Rural Areas</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will provide children with 350 school kits at Al-Fath school in Al-Qanawis district - Al-Hodeida city - Yemen. The kits will contain the most needed stationary for students. Due to the current conflict in Yemen, teachers has not received their salaries since 2015. Therefore, the project is also designed to provide 7 teachers with monthly salary of 50$ for 8 months. Moreover, personal protection equipment will be distributed to take the necessary measures against COVID-19 pandemic.</narrative>
  </description>
